dct_title_s: Carte de France et des frontiéres ä 1/200.000 (Type 1912)
dct_description_sm: Shows Coblenz and surrounding region.; Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights.; Shows railroads, tramways, rivers, canals, bridges, towers, ruins, fortifications, and windmills.; Includes boundary diagram and index maps.
